twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=wordpressdotcom\" title=\"WordPress.com\" class=\"twitter-action\">@wordpressdotcom</a></strong><span><br />WordPress.com</span></span></span>\n<div>Breaking news for CNN, Time &amp; others leads to over 105M WP.com pageviews in one day, most ever recorded</div>\n<div class=\"twitter-actions\"><span class=\"twitter-meta\"><a title=\"tweeted on May 3, 2011 10:35 am\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/wordpressdotcom/status/65469567937413120\" target=\"_blank\">May 3, 2011 10:35 am</a> via <a href=\"http://cotweet.com/?utm_source=sp1\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"blank\">CoTweet</a></span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?in_reply_to=65469567937413120\" class=\"twitter-action twitter-reply-action\" title=\"Reply\"><span><em></em><strong>Reply</strong></span></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/retweet?tweet_id=65469567937413120\" class=\"twitter-action twitter-retweet-action\" title=\"Retweet\"><span><em></em><strong>Retweet</strong></span></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/favorite?tweet_id=65469567937413120\" class=\"twitter-action twitter-favorite-action\" title=\"Favorite\"><span><em></em><strong>Favorite</strong></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><em>Ready to become a <a href=\"http://vip.wordpress.com/\">VIP Services Client</a>? Some of the <a href=\"http://vip.wordpress.com/clients\">world’s biggest brands rely on WordPress.com VIP Services.</a></em></p>\n<br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/wordpresspublishers.wordpress.com/1431/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/wordpresspublishers.wordpress.com/1431/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/wordpresspublishers.wordpress.com/1431/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/wordpresspublishers.wordpress.com/1431/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/wordpresspublishers.w